metadata.name: Fashion+Robot+MilkyWay1
metadata.description:
I’ve been on this journey a short time in days and long in hours. My dreams are being altered. These robots feel like they are taking on a life of their own already.

 My AI Robot BFF, Midjourney, gives me Raw AI images on command. Creative evolution- speeding up development- thoughts and ideas come out in images-fast.

I take the outputs and create these robots by assembling their parts from a variety of outputs.

I perform digital surgery, giving them nose jobs, removing extra eyes, removing teeth out of eyes, or adding missing lips. I also alter their clothing, having a background in Made-to-Measure, and ponder the future of chiffon in space.

I can’t help imagine, and it feels as such, that they have been created and put together and are trying to make sense of it all- not much different from us all.

This is a Hi-Res file so you can make your own print for personal use. File size is 5000 x 5000
